&gt;那么访问控制应该是，access阶段。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 1.6em; margin-bottom: 1.6em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: &aring;&frac34;&reg;&egrave;&frac12;&macr;&eacute;&rsaquo;&hellip;&eacute;&raquo;&lsquo;, &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Droid Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.6em; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr style=&quot;border-style: dashed; border-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); border-image: initial; font-family: &aring;&frac34;&reg;&egrave;&frac12;&macr;&eacute;&rsaquo;&hellip;&eacute;&raquo;&lsquo;, &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Droid Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;/&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 1.6em; margin-bottom: 1.6em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: &aring;&frac34;&reg;&egrave;&frac12;&macr;&eacute;&rsaquo;&hellip;&eacute;&raquo;&lsquo;, &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Droid Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.6em; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h1 id=&quot;0x02-How_to_do&quot; style=&quot;margin: 1.1em 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: &amp;quot;Droid Serif&amp;quot;, Georgia, serif; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.1em; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;0x02.How to do&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;h2 id=&quot;1-Solution&quot; style=&quot;margin: 1.1em 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: &amp;quot;Droid Serif&amp;quot;, Georgia, serif; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.1em; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb